\cot x = \frac1x + \sum_{n=1}^\infty \left(\frac{1}{x+\pi n} + \frac{1}{x-\pi n}\right) = 1 + 2\sum_{n=1}^\infty \frac{x}{x^2 - (\pi n)^2},
\cot x = \lim_{N\to\infty} \sum_{n=-N}^N \frac{1}{x+\pi n}.
